SUMMARY	O
OF	O
THE	O
INVENTION	O
The	O
present	O
invention	O
generally	O
relates	O
to	O
a	O
system	O
for	O
assisting	O
a	O
user	O
in	O
his	O
understanding	O
of	O
a	O
book	O
which	O
is	O
being	O
read	O
or	O
studied	O
and	O
further	O
for	O
